b" pandas trick:

Need to check if two Series contain the same elements?

 Don't do this:
df.A == df.B

 Do this:
df.A.equals(df.B)

 Also works for DataFrames:
df.equals(df2)

equals() properly handles NaNs, whereas == does not

#Python #DataScience #pandas #pandastricks"
